{"tid":139652,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人貼左玻璃隔熱膜","createTime":"2017-03-01T14:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T19:22:25.000Z","uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c9383a104cc2deda1159f0c29fe7cca357e9320","tid":139652,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:54:58.000Z","msg":"遲下收車想貼玻璃隔熱膜<br />\n<br />\n3M果隻3M Crystalline 有冇人做過???<br />\n效果如何?值唔值得做<br />\n<br />\n我問過間都要成$6k冇包天窗 <br />\n有冇平D既介紹/牌子 可以過到驗車<br />\n<br />\n另外 有冇人有平靚正既coating介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972ae594570bbfcd439984e086f67bf16d10fd40","tid":139652,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲下收車想貼玻璃隔熱膜<br />\n<br />\n3M果隻3M Crystalline 有冇人做過???<br />\n效果如何?值唔值得做<br />\n<br />\n我問過間都要成$6k冇包天窗 <br />\n有冇平D既介紹/牌子 可以過到驗車<br />\n<br />\n另外 有冇人有平靚正既coating介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n效果唔錯，泊完街上車嗰陣係明顯覺得冇咁熱。大太陽揸車嗰陣都係覺得冇咁熱。<br />\n我就係做呢隻料，佢都算高隔熱，高透光架喇。<br />\n我做嗰陣特價，4800包全車excl天窗（我係4門sedan,冇天窗）<br />\n驗唔驗到車係睇透光度，詳情問返幫你黐嗰個。我做合法嘅，驗埋吸埋印。"},{"pid":"418fe4c5ec7267428a4a21660c812998a04ff3ad","tid":139652,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:09:27.000Z","msg":"自己整咪得<br />\n買日本yac 一卷兩米 200$卷<br />\n七人車自己一個搞掂<br />\n當然你要有技術<br />\n利申 開車房"},{"pid":"f328900ffb2cdf47f448a911a928bfe646297c5e","tid":139652,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"擇3M啦<br />\n搞玻璃最緊要有認證<br />\n除非你好鐘意小欖嘅驗車師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d8c64d3957a368ab5d42d04a7d4a8f557d739c","tid":139652,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:23:44.000Z","msg":"我就係想一次過 <br />\n過埋驗車唔想煩<br />\n之前見佢$4800 <br />\n依家要$6000<br />\n衡量緊值唔值得貼 <br />\n定係留返d錢整coating好"},{"pid":"0026e7966cc35f8b6c7171babecda29cbd439443","tid":139652,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係想一次過 <br />\n過埋驗車唔想煩<br />\n之前見佢$4800 <br />\n依家要$6000<br />\n衡量緊值唔值得貼 <br />\n定係留返d錢整coating好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係純粹問值唔值可以答你唔值<br />\n值嘅話個廠商自己出啦<br />\n洗要人自己買嘢整<br />\n加上其實冇咩用<br />\n不如留返筆錢整其他嘢"},{"pid":"7e74b073d82593c1ccb5f8c7f6602980ee7ac44d","tid":139652,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我就係想一次過 <br />\n過埋驗車唔想煩<br />\n之前見佢$4800 <br />\n依家要$6000<br />\n衡量緊值唔值得貼 <br />\n定係留返d錢整coating好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係純粹問值唔值可以答你唔值<br />\n值嘅話個廠商自己出啦<br />\n洗要人自己買嘢整<br />\n加上其實冇咩用<br />\n不如留返筆錢整其他嘢</blockquote><br />\n咁我都係唔整住了<br />\nbtw 巴打有冇平靚正既coating介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5800dd91184beed684af1b4d9605a3b86c4facb7","tid":139652,"uid":66201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我就係想一次過 <br />\n過埋驗車唔想煩<br />\n之前見佢$4800 <br />\n依家要$6000<br />\n衡量緊值唔值得貼 <br />\n定係留返d錢整coating好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係純粹問值唔值可以答你唔值<br />\n值嘅話個廠商自己出啦<br />\n洗要人自己買嘢整<br />\n加上其實冇咩用<br />\n不如留返筆錢整其他嘢</blockquote><br />\n咁我都係唔整住了<br />\nbtw 巴打有冇平靚正既coating介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平靚正無可能同時存在<br />\n只可以話如果coating同痴玻璃我會簡痴玻璃"},{"pid":"7358ea31c7dfd7294f00c1bba0a0f34d7da61f1d","tid":139652,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:47:04.000Z